source.name: SNPdb: Haplotype Polymorphism in Polyploid Wheats and their Diploid Ancestors
source.description: This is a tool to discover and map single nucleotide polymorphisms in tetraploid and hexaploid wheat and to characterize genetics and structure of the genepools of wheat and wheat diploid ancestors.
